http://www.thehindu.com/news/national/karnataka/Ponnuraj-to-return-to-State/article13998620.ece

IAS officer V. Ponnuraj is expected to return to the State after a brief stint as private secretary to Union Minister for Law and Justice D.V. Sadananda Gowda.Official sources told The Hindu on Wednesday that Mr. Ponnuraj would be appointed as Managing Director of Karnataka Urban Infrastructure Development and Finance Corporation Ltd. (KUIDFCL). The Union Minister has agreed to relieve Mr. Ponnuraj. The officer will be assigned the task of implementing Smart City and AMRUT projects of the Union government, according to sources.